*** Aesthetics
:PROPERTIES:
:ID:       6810a2cb-dacd-4ff7-9d2f-be054a717be4
:END:
- *Philosophy of Art*
- came from the greek word "/aesthetikos/", which means *perceptive of things*.
- concern with the essence of perception, objective, judgement of beauty and nature of art.
